<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>五运六气 · 完全教程</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@300;400;600;700;900&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500&family=Ma+Shan+Zheng&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #1a1008;
    --vermillion: #c0392b;
    --gold: #b8860b;
    --gold-light: #d4a017;
    --jade: #2e7d5e;
    --sky: #2c6e8a;
    --earth: #8b5e3c;
    --parchment: #f5f0e8;
    --parchment-dark: #ede4d3;
    --parchment-deeper: #d9ccb5;
    --fog: #f9f6f0;
    --metal: #6b7280;
    --wood: #4a7c59;
    --fire: #b94040;
    --water: #2c5f8a;
    --earth-col: #9c7040;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', serif;
    background: var(--parchment);
    color: var(--ink);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* Texture overlay */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23b8860b' fill-opacity='0.04'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, rgba(44,110,138,0.12) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(192,57,43,0.10) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(184,134,11,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%),
      var(--parchment);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '天';
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px; left: -30px;
    font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
    font-size: 300px;
    color: rgba(184,134,11,0.06);
    line-height: 1;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: '地';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -40px; right: -20px;
    font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
    font-size: 300px;
    color: rgba(44,110,138,0.05);
    line-height: 1;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
    font-size: clamp(60px, 12vw, 120px);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 8px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 rgba(184,134,11,0.15);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(16px, 2.5vw, 22px);
    color: var(--earth);
    margin-top: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 32px auto 0;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 2;
    color: #5a4a3a;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 32px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    animation: bounce 2s infinite;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .scroll-hint::after {
    content: '↓';
    font-size: 20px;
  }
  @keyframes bounce {
    0%,100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(8px); }
  }

  /* ── NAVIGATION ── */
  .nav-bar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(245,240,232,0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--parchment-deeper);
    padding: 0 24px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .nav-bar a {
    padding: 14px 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--earth);
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .nav-bar a:hover { color: var(--vermillion); border-bottom-color: var(--vermillion); }

  /* ── SECTIONS ── */
  .section {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 24px;
  }

  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .section-num {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--parchment);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
    font-size: 24px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .section-title span {
    color: var(--vermillion);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--metal);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* ── DIVIDERS ── */
  .divider {
    border: none;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--parchment-deeper), transparent);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── PROSE ── */
  .prose {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 2;
    color: #3a2e20;
  }
  .prose p { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .prose strong { color: var(--vermillion); font-weight: 600; }
  .prose em { color: var(--sky); font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; }

  /* ── CONCEPT CARDS ── */
  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--parchment-deeper);
    padding: 24px 20px;
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .card-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #5a4a3a;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .card.wood { border-top: 3px solid var(--wood); }
  .card.fire { border-top: 3px solid var(--fire); }
  .card.earth { border-top: 3px solid var(--earth-col); }
  .card.metal { border-top: 3px solid var(--metal); }
  .card.water { border-top: 3px solid var(--water); }

  /* ── GANZHI TABLE ── */
  .gz-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 24px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .gz-table th {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--parchment);
    padding: 12px 16px;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .gz-table td {
    padding: 10px 16px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--parchment-deeper);
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .gz-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: var(--parchment-dark); }
  .gz-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(184,134,11,0.1); }

  /* ── FORMULA BOX ── */
  .formula-box {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--parchment);
    padding: 28px 32px;
    margin: 24px 0;
    position: relative;
    font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
  }
  .formula-box::before {
    content: '◆';
    position: absolute;
    top: -8px; left: 20px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  .formula-title {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .formula-content {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 2.2;
    color: #e8dcc8;
  }
  .formula-content .hl { color: var(--gold-light); font-weight: 600; }

  /* ── TIMELINE ── */
  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    margin: 32px 0;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--vermillion), var(--gold), var(--jade));
  }

  .tl-item {
    position: relative;
    padding: 0 0 32px 32px;
  }
  .tl-item::before {
    content: attr(data-num);
    position: absolute;
    left: -14px;
    top: 0;
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    background: var(--parchment);
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 24px;
  }

  .tl-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .tl-content {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #4a3a2a;
  }

  /* ── THE STAR ── */
  .birth-banner {
    background: var(--ink);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 48px 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .birth-banner::before {
    content: '命';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
    font-size: 300px;
    color: rgba(184,134,11,0.06);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .birth-banner h2 {
    font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
    font-size: 42px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .birth-banner p {
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.75);
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* ── RESULT CARDS ── */
  .result-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .result-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--parchment-deeper);
    padding: 28px 24px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .result-card::after {
    content: attr(data-bg);
    position: absolute;
    right: -10px; bottom: -20px;
    font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
    font-size: 80px;
    opacity: 0.06;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .rc-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--metal);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .rc-main {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .rc-main span {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--metal);
    margin-left: 8px;
  }
  .rc-detail {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #5a4a3a;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--parchment-deeper);
    padding-top: 12px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .rc-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 2px 10px;
    font-size: 11px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .rc-tag.excess { background: rgba(192,57,43,0.1); color: var(--vermillion); }
  .rc-tag.deficient { background: rgba(44,110,138,0.1); color: var(--sky); }
  .rc-tag.neutral { background: rgba(155,119,80,0.1); color: var(--earth); }

  /* ── HEALTH ANALYSIS ── */
  .health-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .health-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .health-card {
    padding: 20px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    background: white;
  }
  .health-card.warn { border-color: var(--vermillion); }
  .health-card.info { border-color: var(--sky); }
  .health-card.good { border-color: var(--jade); }

  .hc-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .hc-body {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #4a3a2a;
  }

  /* ── WUYUN TABLE ── */
  .wuyun-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2px;
    margin: 16px 0;
  }
  .wy-cell {
    padding: 16px 12px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    border: 1px solid var(--parchment-deeper);
    background: white;
  }
  .wy-cell.active {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--parchment);
    border-color: var(--ink);
  }
  .wy-cell.active .wy-name { color: var(--gold); }
  .wy-num { font-size: 11px; color: var(--metal); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .wy-name { font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .wy-period { font-size: 11px; color: var(--metal); }
  .wy-cell.active .wy-period { color: rgba(245,240,232,0.6); }
  .wy-cell.active .wy-num { color: var(--gold-light); }

  /* ── LIUQI TABLE ── */
  .liuqi-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    margin: 16px 0;
  }
  .lq-cell {
    padding: 14px 8px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--parchment-deeper);
    background: white;
  }
  .lq-cell.active { background: var(--sky); color: white; border-color: var(--sky); }
  .lq-cell.active .lq-name { color: white; }
  .lq-cell.active .lq-period { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
  .lq-num { font-size: 10px; color: var(--metal); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .lq-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; color: var(--ink); }
  .lq-period { font-size: 10px; color: var(--metal); }

  /* ── SCOPE ── */
  .scope-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }
  .scope-card {
    background: var(--fog);
    border: 1px solid var(--parchment-deeper);
    padding: 24px 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .scope-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .scope-title { font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .scope-body { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8; color: #5a4a3a; }

  /* ── QUOTE ── */
  .big-quote {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 24px 28px;
    margin: 32px 0;
    background: rgba(184,134,11,0.05);
    font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 2;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .big-quote cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  /* ── CHARM SECTION ── */
  .charm-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }
  .charm-card {
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 28px 24px;
    color: var(--parchment);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .charm-card::before {
    content: attr(data-ch);
    position: absolute;
    right: -5px; bottom: -15px;
    font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
    font-size: 80px;
    opacity: 0.1;
    color: var(--gold);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cc-title { color: var(--gold); font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .cc-body { font-size: 13px; line-height: 2; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.8); }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  .footer {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 24px;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    line-height: 2;
  }
  .footer span { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ── MISC ── */
  .highlight-box {
    background: rgba(192,57,43,0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.2);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--vermillion);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin: 20px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 2;
    color: #3a2020;
  }
  .step-list { counter-reset: step; }
  .step-item {
    counter-increment: step;
    padding: 14px 20px 14px 60px;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--parchment-deeper);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }
  .step-item::before {
    content: counter(step);
    position: absolute;
    left: 16px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    background: var(--vermillion);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 28px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .step-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .step-title { font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 4px; }

  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 3px 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    border: 1px solid;
    margin: 3px;
  }
  .tag.wood { border-color: var(--wood); color: var(--wood); }
  .tag.fire { border-color: var(--fire); color: var(--fire); }
  .tag.earth { border-color: var(--earth-col); color: var(--earth-col); }
  .tag.metal { border-color: var(--metal); color: var(--metal); }
  .tag.water { border-color: var(--water); color: var(--water); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .wuyun-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    .liuqi-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    .health-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge">中医经典理论 · 完全教程</div>
  <h1>五运六气</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">天地之大纪，人神之通应</p>
  <p class="hero-desc">
    五运六气，是中医学中运用阴阳五行、天干地支推演<br>
    天地气候变化规律及其对人体生命影响的系统理论。<br>
    源于《黄帝内经·素问》七篇大论，历经两千年传承。
  </p>
  <div class="scroll-hint">向下探索</div>
</section>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="nav-bar">
  <a href="#origin">渊源</a>
  <a href="#concept">核心概念</a>
  <a href="#wuyun">五运详解</a>
  <a href="#liuqi">六气详解</a>
  <a href="#calc">推算方法</a>
  <a href="#example">命例解析</a>
  <a href="#scope">适用范围</a>
  <a href="#charm">魅力所在</a>
</nav>

<!-- SECTION 1: ORIGIN -->
<section class="section" id="origin">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-num">源</div>
    <div>
      <div class="section-title">理论<span>渊源</span></div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">THE ORIGIN</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="prose">
    <p>五运六气学说，简称"运气学说"，是古代中国哲学与医学的结晶。其核心思想见于《黄帝内经·素问》的七篇大论：<strong>天元纪大论、五运行大论、六微旨大论、气交变大论、五常政大论、六元正纪大论、至真要大论</strong>。</p>
    <p>这一理论建立在"<em>天人相应</em>"的哲学基础上——天地之间的气候变化，与人体的生理病理息息相通。古人观察到宇宙存在周期性节律，通过<strong>干支纪年</strong>体系，将这些节律编码为可计算的推演系统。</p>
  </div>

